      { q: 'My community pavers have faded unevenly — can a reseal even them out?', a: 'Yes. The deep clean lifts the ground-in grime and mold that make the fade look patchy, and the sealer brings the color back to a consistent finish across the whole driveway, so it matches the rest of the street again.' },
