      { q: 'Do I have to reseal a large pool deck as often as a driveway?', a: 'A pool deck near the water and constant sun usually wants resealing every two to three years, a driveway every three to four. We often clean and seal both together so the whole property stays on one maintenance cycle.' },
      { q: 'What does paver cleaning and sealing cost?', a: 'It depends on the square footage and the condition of the pavers, which is why the on-site visit and written estimate are free and itemized. Financing through Wisetack is available so the budget does not decide the timeline.' },
