      { q: 'Black mold keeps coming back on my pool deck — can you clean and seal it off?', a: 'Yes. The deep clean strips the mold off the surface, and the sealer makes the pavers easier to rinse and slower to grow it back. Near the water it will return over time, so a reseal every couple of years keeps ahead of it.' },
      { q: 'Heavy rain has washed the sand out of my joints — how do you fix that?', a: 'We refill the joints with polymeric sand that hardens into a firm bond, so it holds through the summer downpours far better than the loose sand that washed out, and it locks out the weeds and ants that had moved in.' },
